{"data":[{"name":"91:1","price":"சூரியன் மீது சத்தியமாக! அதன் பகல் மீது சத்தியமாக! (ழுஹா: பகல், முற்பகல், வெளிச்சம்)","arabic":"وَٱلشَّمۡسِ وَضُحَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6044,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-shamsi waḍuḥāhā ","translations":["By the sun","and its brightness","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-shamsi","waḍuḥāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1070],[2,1070,2575]]}},{"name":"91:2","price":"சந்திரன் மீது சத்தியமாக, அதை (-சூரியனை) அது பின்தொடரும்போது!","arabic":"وَٱلۡقَمَرِ إِذَا تَلَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6045,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-qamari idhā talāhā ","translations":["And the moon","when","it follows it","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-qamari","idhā","talāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1050],[2,1050,1630],[3,1630,3095]]}},{"name":"91:3","price":"பகலின் மீது சத்தியமாக, அதை (-சூரியனை) அது வெளிப்படுத்தும்போது (வெளிச்சப்படுத்தும் போது)!","arabic":"وَٱلنَّهَارِ إِذَا جَلَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6046,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-nahāri idhā jallāhā ","translations":["And the day","when","it displays it","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-nahāri","idhā","jallāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2240],[2,2240,2870],[3,2870,4345]]}},{"name":"91:4","price":"இரவின் மீது சத்தியமாக, அதை (-சூரியனை) அது மூடும்போது!","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا يَغۡشَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6047,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-al-layli idhā yaghshāhā ","translations":["And the night","when","it covers it","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-al-layli","idhā","yaghshāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,1750],[3,1750,3315]]}},{"name":"91:5","price":"வானத்தின் மீது சத்தியமாக! அதை அமைத்தவன் மீது சத்தியமாக!","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ وَمَا بَنَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6048,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-samāi wamā banāhā ","translations":["And the heaven","and (He) Who","constructed it","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-samāi","wamā","banāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2670],[2,2670,3340],[3,3340,4575]]}},{"name":"91:6","price":"பூமியின் மீது சத்தியமாக! அதை விரித்தவன் மீது சத்தியமாக!","arabic":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ وَمَا طَحَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6049,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-arḍi wamā ṭaḥāhā ","translations":["And the earth","and by (He) Who","spread it","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-arḍi","wamā","ṭaḥāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1080],[2,1080,1650],[3,1650,2935]]}},{"name":"91:7","price":"ஆன்மாவின் மீது சத்தியமாக! அதை சீர்படுத்தியவன் மீது சத்தியமாக!","arabic":"وَنَفۡسٖ وَمَا سَوَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6050,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wanafsin wamā sawwāhā ","translations":["And (the) soul","and (He) Who","proportioned it","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wanafsin","wamā","sawwāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1750],[2,1750,2260],[3,2260,3835]]}},{"name":"91:8","price":"ஆக, அவன் அதன் தீமையையும் அதன் நன்மையையும் அதற்கு அறிவித்தான்.","arabic":"فَأَلۡهَمَهَا فُجُورَهَا وَتَقۡوَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6051,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-alhamahā fujūrahā wataqwāhā ","translations":["And He inspired it","(to distinguish) its wickedness","and its righteousness","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-alhamahā","fujūrahā","wataqwāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1460],[2,1460,2740],[3,2740,4575]]}},{"name":"91:9","price":"(நிராகரிப்பிலிருந்தும் பாவங்களிலிருந்தும் பாதுகாத்து, நல்லமல்களை கொண்டு) யாரை அல்லாஹ் பரிசுத்தப்படுத்தினானோ அவர் திட்டமாக வெற்றிபெற்றார்.","arabic":"قَدۡ أَفۡلَحَ مَن زَكَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6052,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"qad aflaḥa man zakkāhā ","translations":["Indeed","he succeeds","who","purifies it","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["qad","aflaḥa","man","zakkāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,1280],[3,1280,2220],[4,2220,3705]]}},{"name":"91:10","price":"யாருக்கு அதை (-அவரது ஆன்மாவை பாவத்தில்) அல்லாஹ் மறைத்துவிட்டானோ (-வழிகேட்டில், பாவத்தில் விட்டுவிட்டானோ) அவர் திட்டமாக நஷ்டமடைந்தார்.","arabic":"وَقَدۡ خَابَ مَن دَسَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6053,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"waqad khāba man dassāhā ","translations":["And indeed","he fails","who","buries it","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["waqad","khāba","man","dassāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,540],[2,540,1290],[3,1290,2330],[4,2330,3835]]}},{"name":"91:11","price":"ஸமூது சமுதாயம் தன் அழிச்சாட்டியத்தால் (தூதரைப்) பொய்ப்பித்தது.","arabic":"كَذَّبَتۡ ثَمُودُ بِطَغۡوَىٰهَآ","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6054,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"kadhabat thamūdu biṭaghwāhā ","translations":["Denied","Thamud","by their transgression","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["kadhabat","thamūdu","biṭaghwāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1050],[2,1050,1920],[3,1920,3585]]}},{"name":"91:12","price":"அதன் தீயவன் புறப்பட்டபோது,","arabic":"إِذِ ٱنۢبَعَثَ أَشۡقَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6055,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"idhi inbaʿatha ashqāhā ","translations":["When","(was) sent forth","(the) most wicked of them","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["idhi","inbaʿatha","ashqāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,500],[2,500,1970],[3,1970,3365]]}},{"name":"91:13","price":"ஆக, அல்லாஹ்வின் தூதர் (-ஸாலிஹ்) அவர்களுக்குக் கூறினார்: “அல்லாஹ்வுடைய பெண் ஒட்டகத்தையும் அது நீர் பருகுவதையும் தடை செய்யாதீர்!’’","arabic":"فَقَالَ لَهُمۡ رَسُولُ ٱللَّهِ نَاقَةَ ٱللَّهِ وَسُقۡيَٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6056,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"faqāla lahum rasūlu al-lahi nāqata al-lahi wasuq'yāhā ","translations":["But said","to them","(the) Messenger","(of) Allah","(It is the) she-camel","(of) Allah","and her drink","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["faqāla","lahum","rasūlu","al-lahi","nāqata","al-lahi","wasuq'yāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,1420],[3,1420,2340],[4,2340,3270],[5,3270,4070],[6,4070,5030],[7,5030,6745]]}},{"name":"91:14","price":"ஆக, அவர்கள் அவரைப் பொய்ப்பித்தார்கள். இன்னும் அ(ந்த ஒட்டகத்)தை (அறுத்து) கொன்றுவிட்டார்கள். ஆகவே, அவர்களின் பாவத்தினால் அவர்களுடைய இறைவன் அவர்கள் மீது கடுமையான தண்டனையை இறக்கினான். அ(ந்த சமுதாயத்)தை (அதில் உள்ள அனைவரையும் தண்டனையில்) சமமாக்கினான். (ஒட்டகத்தை கொன்றவன் ஒருவனாக இருந்தாலும் அதை எல்லோரும் பொருந்திக் கொண்டதால் அந்த சமுதாயத்தில் இருந்த எல்லோருக்கும் அதே தண்டனையை கொடுத்து அழித்துவிட்டான்.)","arabic":"فَكَذَّبُوهُ فَعَقَرُوهَا فَدَمۡدَمَ عَلَيۡهِمۡ رَبُّهُم بِذَنۢبِهِمۡ فَسَوَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6057,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fakadhabūhu faʿaqarūhā fadamdama ʿalayhim rabbuhum bidhanbihim fasawwāhā ","translations":["But they denied him","and they hamstrung her","So destroyed","them","their Lord","for their sin","and leveled them","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["fakadhabūhu","faʿaqarūhā","fadamdama","ʿalayhim","rabbuhum","bidhanbihim","fasawwāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1480],[2,1480,2980],[3,2980,4080],[4,4080,5080],[5,5080,6790],[6,6790,8680],[7,8680,10555]]}},{"name":"91:15","price":"இன்னும், அவன் அதன் முடிவைப் பயப்பட மாட்டான்.","arabic":"وَلَا يَخَافُ عُقۡبَٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6058,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"walā yakhāfu ʿuq'bāhā ","translations":["And not","He fears","its consequences","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","yakhāfu","ʿuq'bāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,520],[2,520,1740],[3,1740,5365]]}}],"chapter":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams","Chapter Ash-Shams","Shams","Surah Shams","Chapter Shams","Ash Shams","Surah Ash Shams","Chapter Ash Shams","Surah 91","Chapter 91","The Sun","الشمس"],"version":{"key":"tamil_omar","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ta","version":"1.0.2","last_update":1670915064,"title":"Tamil Translation - Omar Sharif","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Tamil by Sh. Omar Sharif ibn Abdusalam"}}